ream_000005\", \"pt\": \"Nós temos que tratar disto como se fosse acidental.\", \"source\": \"Helsinki-NLP/opus-100/en-pt/train\"}\n./results/02_final_training/final_training_20260620T053855Z/data_splits/train.jsonl:7:{\"en\": \"Come here, honey.\", \"id\": \"opus100_stream_000006\", \"pt\": \"Vem aqui, querida.\", \"source\": \"Helsinki-NLP/opus-100/en-pt/train\"}\n./results/02_final_training/final_training_20260620T053855Z/data_splits/train.jsonl:8:{\"en\": \"Terms specifying recognised geological time units.\", \"id\": \"opus100_stream_000007\", \"pt\": \"Termos que especificam unidades geológicas temporais reconhecidas.\", \"source\": \"Helsinki-NLP/opus-100/en-pt/train\"}\n./results/02_final_training/final_training_20260620T053855Z/data_splits/train.jsonl:9:{\"en\": \"Ethylene glycol (ethanediol)\", \"id\": \"opus100_stream_000008\", \"pt\": \"Etilenoglicol (etanodiol)\", \"source\": \"Helsinki-NLP/opus-100/en-pt/train\"}\n./results/02_final_training/final_training_20260620T053855Z/data_splits/train.jsonl:10:{\"en\": \"You are killing me.\", \"id\": \"opus100_stream_000009\", \"pt\": \"Estás a dar cabo de mim.\", \"source\": \"Helsinki-NLP/opus-100/en-pt/train\"}\n./results/02_final_training/final_training_20260620T053855Z/data_splits/train.jsonl:11:{\"en\": \"Hey, honeybear, hi!\", \"id\": \"opus100_stream_000010\", \"pt\": \"Olá ursinho.\", \"source\": \"Helsinki-NLP/opus-100/en-pt/train\"}\n./results/02_final_training/final_training_20260620T053855Z/data_splits/train.jsonl:12:{\"en\": \"For example, the social dimension of the common fisheries policy has developed favourably in recent times, but is not commensurate with the large-scale adjustments proposed by the Commission under MGP IV.\", \"id\": \"opus100_stream_000011\", \"pt\": \"Por exemplo, a abordagem social da política comum da pesca evoluiu favoravelmente nos últimos tempos, embora não esteja ainda à altura da dimensão do ajustamento proposto pela Comissão no POP IV.\", \"source\": \"Helsinki-NLP/opus-100/en-pt/train\"}\n./results/02_final_training/final_training_20260620T053855Z/data_splits/train.jsonl:13:{\"en\": \"Yeah, try again.\", \"id\": \"opus100_stream_000012\", \"pt\": \"É? Tente de novo.\", \"source\": \"Helsinki-NLP/opus-100/en-pt/train\"}\n./results/02_final_training/final_training_20260620T053855Z/data_splits/train.jsonl:14:{\"en\": \"They, they never told me what was in it.\", \"id\": \"opus100_stream_000013\", \"pt\": \"Eles nunca me disseram o que era.\", \"source\": \"Helsinki-NLP/opus-100/en-pt/train\"}\n./results/02_final_training/final_training_20260620T053855Z/data_splits/train.jsonl:15:{\"en\": \"What have you done?\", \"id\": \"opus100_stream_000014\", \"pt\": \"Que fizestes de mim?\", \"source\": \"Helsinki-NLP/opus-100/en-pt/train\"}\n./results/02_final_training/final_training_20260620T053855Z/data_splits/train.jsonl:16:{\"en\": \"I'll tell you what:\", \"id\": \"opus100_stream_000015\", \"pt\": \"O que tens feito para o Shack.\", \"source\": \"Helsinki-NLP/opus-100/en-pt/train\"}\n./results/02_final_training/final_training_20260620T053855Z/data_splits/train.jsonl:17:{\"en\": \"Okay, so, Tommie... You were right.\", \"id\": \"opus100_stream_000016\", \"pt\": \"Então Tommie... estavas certo.\", \"source\": \"Helsinki-NLP/opus-100/en-pt/train\"}\n./results/02_final_training/final_training_20260620T053855Z/data_splits/train.jsonl:18:{\"en\": \"Mechanism of action:\", \"id\": \"opus100_stream_000017\", \"pt\": \"Mecanismo de acção:\", \"source\": \"Helsinki-NLP/opus-100/en-pt/train\"}\n./results/02_final_training/final_training_20260620T053855Z/data_splits/train.jsonl:19:{\"en\": \"He doesn't deserve that.\", \"id\": \"opus100_stream_000018\", \"pt\": \"Näo o merece.\", \"source\": \"Helsinki-NLP/opus-100/en-pt/train\"}\n./results/02_final_training/final_training_20260620T053855Z/data_splits/train.jsonl:20:{\"en\": \"Bailiff? Remove the jury.\", \"id\": \"opus100_stream_000019\", \"pt\": \"Oficial de justiça, retire o júri.\", \"source\": \"Helsinki-NLP/opus-100/en-pt/train\"}\n./results/02_final_training/final_training_20260620T053855Z/data_splits/train.jsonl:21:{\"en\": \"Just do what she says.\", \"id\": \"opus100_stream_000020\", \"pt\": \"- Faz o que ela diz.\", \"source\": \"Helsinki-NLP/opus-100/en-pt/train\"}\n./results/02_final_training/final_training_20260620T053855Z/data_splits/train.jsonl:22:{\"en\": \"OH, NO, COUNT ME OUT.\", \"id\": \"opus100_stream_000021\", \"pt\": \"Quem te ensinou? - A mamãe.\", \"source\": \"Helsinki-NLP/opus-100/en-pt/train\"}\n./results/02_final_training/final_training_20260620T053855Z/data_splits/train.jsonl:23:{\"en\": \"What am I to do in Northumbria with an army of two, a nun and a rag-arse?\", \"id\": \"opus100_stream_000022\", \"pt\": \"Que farei em Nortúmbria com um exército de dois: uma freira e um cu de trapos?\", \"source\": \"Helsinki-NLP/opus-100/en-pt/train\"}\n./results/02_final_training/final_training_20260620T053855Z/data_splits/train.jsonl:24:{\"en\": \"That's the hardest part.\", \"id\": \"opus100_stream_000023\", \"pt\": \"Isso é o mais difícil.\", \"source\": \"Helsinki-NLP/opus-100/en-pt/train\"}\n./results/02_final_training/final_training_20260620T053855Z/data_splits/train.jsonl:25:{\"en\": \"You haven't finished the story about your grandson.\", \"id\": \"opus100_stream_000024\", \"pt\": \"Você não terminou a história do seu neto.\", \"source\": \"Helsinki-NLP/opus-100/en-pt/train\"}\n./results/02_final_training/final_training_20260620T053855Z/data_splits/train.jsonl:26:{\"en\": \"Why did you tell me that story?\", \"id\": \"opus100_stream_000025\", \"pt\": \"Por que me contou essa história?\", \"source\": \"Helsinki-NLP/opus-100/en-pt/train\"}\n./results/02_final_training/final_training_20260620T053855Z/data_splits/train.jsonl:27:{\"en\": \"She calls us.\", \"id\": \"opus100_stream_000026\", \"pt\": \"Ela é que nos liga.\", \"source\": \"Helsinki-NLP/opus-100/en-pt/train\"}\n./results/02_final_training/final_training_20260620T053855Z/data_splits/train.jsonl:28:{\"en\": \"-I'll check on Epps.\", \"id\": \"opus100_stream_000027\", \"pt\": \"- Vou ter com a Epps.\", \"source\": \"Helsinki-NLP/opus-100/en-pt/train\"}\n./results/02_final_training/final_training_20260620T053855Z/data_splits/train.jsonl:29:{\"en\": \"What is that?\", \"id\": \"opus100_stream_000028\", \"pt\": \"O que é isto?\", \"source\": \"Helsinki-NLP/opus-100/en-pt/train\"}\n./results/02_final_training/final_training_20260620T053855Z/data_splits/train.jsonl:30:{\"en\": \"Bad tempers... and a lot of strike talk.\", \"id\": \"opus100_stream_000029\", \"pt\": \"Mau ambiente... e muitas conversas sobre greve.\", \"source\": \"Helsinki-NLP/opus-100/en-pt/train\"}\n./results/02_final_training/final_training_20260620T053855Z/data_splits/train.jsonl:31:{\"en\": \"Here she comes.\", \"id\": \"opus100_stream_000030\", \"pt\": \"Ali vem ela.\", \"source\": \"Helsinki-NLP/opus-100/en-pt/train\"}\n./results/02_final_training/final_training_20260620T053855Z/data_splits/train.jsonl:32:{\"en\": \"In the context of Article 10 of Directive 92/102/EEC, the Joint Veterinary Committee shall be responsible for coordination where any electronic identification systems are set up.\", \"id\": \"opus100_stream_000031\", \"pt\": \"No âmbito do artigo 10.o da Directiva 92/102/CEE, a coordenação para a eventual aplicação de dispositivos electrónicos de identificação será da competência do Comité Misto Veterinário.\", \"source\": \"Helsinki-NLP/opus-100/en-pt/train\"}\n./results/02_final_training/final_training_20260620T053855Z/data_splits/train.jsonl:33:{\"en\": \"- You trick.\", \"id\": \"opus100_stream_000032\", \"pt\": \"Prostituis-te.\", \"source\": \"Helsinki-NLP/opus-100/en-pt/train\"}\n./results/02_final_training/final_training_20260620T053855Z/data_splits/train.jsonl:34:{\"en\": \"What happened to your head?\", \"id\": \"opus100_stream_000033\", \"pt\": \"O que aconteceu à tua cabeça?\", \"source\": \"Helsinki-NLP/opus-100/en-pt/train\"}\n./results/02_final_training/final_training_20260620T053855Z/data_splits/train.jsonl:35:{\"en\": \"Adopted by the Commission on 9 December.\", \"id\": \"opus100_stream_000034\", \"pt\": \"Adopção pela Comissão em 9 de Dezembro.\", \"source\": \"Helsinki-NLP/opus-100/en-pt/train\"}\n./results/02_final_training/final_training_20260620T053855Z/data_splits/train.jsonl:36:{\"en\": \"They got all the glass out.\", \"id\": \"opus100_stream_000035\", \"pt\": \"- Sim, estou bem. Eles tiraram o vidro.\", \"source\": \"Helsinki-NLP/opus-100/en-pt/train\"}\n./results/02_final_training/final_training_20260620T053855Z/data_splits/train.jsonl:37:{\"en\": \"That's crazy.\", \"id\": \"opus100_stream_000036\", \"pt\": \"Isso é uma loucura.\", \"source\": \"Helsinki-NLP/opus-100/en-pt/train\"}\n./results/02_final_training/final_training_20260620T053855Z/data_splits/train.jsonl:38:{\"en\": \"Uncontrolled hypertension.\", \"id\": \"opus100_stream_000037\", \"pt\": \"Hipertensão não controlada.\", \"source\": \"Helsinki-NLP/opus-100/en-pt/train\"}\n./results/02_final_training/final_training_20260620T053855Z/data_splits/train.jsonl:39:{\"en\": \"It would be improper for us to reveal cases which we are looking into on our own initiative and there are very good reasons therefore to stick to our policy.\", \"id\": \"opus100_stream_000038\", \"pt\": \"Seria incorrecto da nossa parte revelar casos que estamos a investigar por iniciativa própria e, portanto, temos razões muito válidas para prosseguirmos sem alterações a nossa política.\", \"source\": \"Helsinki-NLP/opus-100/en-pt/train\"}\n./results/02_final_training/final_training_20260620T053855Z/data_splits/train.jsonl:40:{\"en\": \"List of items (3)\", \"id\": \"opus100_stream_000039\", \"pt\": \"List of items (3)\", \"source\": \"Helsinki-NLP/opus-100/en-pt/train\"}\n./results/02_final_training/final_training_20260620T053855Z/data_splits/train.jsonl:41:{\"en\": \"Not a bad fit.\", \"id\": \"opus100_stream_000040\", \"pt\": \"Não ficam mal.\", \"source\": \"Helsinki-NLP/opus-100/en-pt/train\"}\n./results/02_final_training/final_training_20260620T053855Z/data_splits/train.jsonl:42:{\"en\": \"-105 200 120 a) issuing charges and redemption premiums\", \"id\": \"opus100_stream_000041\", \"pt\": \"­105 200 120 a) despesas de emissão e prémios de reembolso . . .\", \"source\": \"Helsinki-NLP/opus-100/en-pt/train\"}\n./results/02_final_training/final_training_20260620T053855Z/data_splits/train.jsonl:43:{\"en\": \"I've wanted to shank that little calypso kid ever since I first met him.\", \"id\": \"opus100_stream_000042\", \"pt\": \"Tenho desejado desancar aquele puto desde que o conheci.\", \"source\": \"Helsinki-NLP/opus-100/en-pt/train\"}\n./results/02_final_training/final_training_20260620T053855Z/data_splits/train.jsonl:44:{\"en\": \"Having regard to the Treaty establishing the European Community,\", \"id\": \"opus100_stream_000043\", \"pt\": \"Tendo em conta o Tratado que institui a Comunidade Europeia,\", \"source\": \"Helsinki-NLP/opus-100/en-pt/train\"}\n./results/02_final_training/final_training_20260620T053855Z/data_splits/train.jsonl:45:{\"en\": \"Last night when I put the girls to bed, I told them how big your heart was.\", \"id\": \"opus100_stream_000044\", \"pt\": \"A noite passada, quando deitei as meninas, disse-lhes que tens um coração gigante.\", \"source\": \"Helsinki-NLP/opus-100/en-pt/train\"}\n./results/02_final_training/final_training_20260620T053855Z/data_splits/train.jsonl:46:{\"en\": \"It is therefore critical to assess how a private borrower would have analysed the Obligation and the maintenance of the Obligation over time [55].\", \"id\": \"opus100_stream_000045\", \"pt\": \"É, portanto, fundamental avaliar a forma como um mutuário privado teria analisado a Obrigação e a respectiva manutenção ao longo do tempo [55].\", \"source\": \"Helsinki-NLP/opus-100/en-pt/train\"}\n./results/02_final_training/final_training_20260620T053855Z/data_splits/train.jsonl:47:{\"en\": \"In my view sufficient account has not been taken of this and that is why I have voted against.\", \"id\": \"opus100_stream_000046\", \"pt\": \"Penso que isto não foi suficientemente levado em conta, razão pela qual votei contra.\", \"source\": \"Helsinki-NLP/opus-100/en-pt/train\"}\n./results/02_final_training/final_training_20260620T053855Z/data_splits/train.jsonl:48:{\"en\": \"-What is it?\", \"id\": \"opus100_stream_000047\", \"pt\": \"-O que estás a fazer?\", \"source\": \"Helsinki-NLP/opus-100/en-pt/train\"}\n./results/02_final_training/final_training_20260620T053855Z/data_splits/train.jsonl:49:{\"en\": \"- I see the bus!\", \"id\": \"opus100_stream_000048\", \"pt\": \"- estou vendo!\", \"source\": \"Helsinki-NLP/opus-100/en-pt/train\"}\n./results/02_final_training/final_training_20260620T053855Z/data_splits/train.jsonl:50:{\"en\": \"Now why would Winston keep that from us?\", \"id\": \"opus100_stream_000049\", \"pt\": \"O Winston escondeu-nos isso porquê?\", \"source\": \"Helsinki-NLP/opus-100/en-pt/train\"}\n./results/02_final_training/final_training_20260620T053855Z/data_splits/train.jsonl:51:{\"en\": \"I'm with the Crime Lab.\", \"id\": \"opus100_stream_000050\", \"pt\": \"Eu sou do CSI.\", \"source\": \"Helsinki-NLP/opus-100/en-pt/train\"}\n./results/02_final_training/final_training_20260620T053855Z/data_splits/train.jsonl:52:{\"en\": \"I'm concerned he may have gotten hurt or...\", \"id\": \"opus100_stream_000051\", \"pt\": \"Preocupa-me que possa estar ferido, ou...\", \"source\": \"Helsinki-NLP/opus-100/en-pt/train\"}\n./results/02_final_training/final_training_20260620T053855Z/data_splits/train.jsonl:53:{\"en\": \"Where are the girls?\", \"id\": \"opus100_stream_000052\", \"pt\": \"Onde estão as raparigas? - Quatro horas e ainda nada.\", \"source\": \"Helsinki-NLP/opus-100/en-pt/train\"}\n./results/02_final_training/final_training_20260620T053855Z/data_splits/train.jsonl:54:{\"en\": \"We'll bushwhack 'em good.\", \"id\": \"opus100_stream_000053\", \"pt\": \"Vão ver que rica emboscada.\", \"source\": \"Helsinki-NLP/opus-100/en-pt/train\"}\n./results/02_final_training/final_training_20260620T053855Z/data_splits/train.jsonl:55:{\"en\": \"She's not breathing.\", \"id\": \"opus100_stream_000054\", \"pt\": \"Não está a respirar.\", \"source\": \"Helsinki-NLP/opus-100/en-pt/train\"}\n./results/02_final_training/final_training_20260620T053855Z/data_splits/train.jsonl:56:{\"en\": \"Yeah, well...\", \"id\": \"opus100_stream_000055\", \"pt\": \"Pois, bem...\", \"source\": \"Helsinki-NLP/opus-100/en-pt/train\"}\n./results/02_final_training/final_training_20260620T053855Z/data_splits/train.jsonl:57:{\"en\": \"- Is that right?\", \"id\": \"opus100_stream_000056\", \"pt\": \"Esta é o Raymond.\", \"source\": \"Helsinki-NLP/opus-100/en-pt/train\"}\n./results/02_final_training/final_training_20260620T053855Z/data_splits/train.jsonl:58:{\"en\": \"And look where you ideas got us.\", \"id\": \"opus100_stream_000057\", \"pt\": \"Olha no que deu.\", \"source\": \"Helsinki-NLP/opus-100/en-pt/train\"}\n./results/02_final_training/final_training_20260620T053855Z/data_splits/train.jsonl:59:{\"en\": \"You've lost a lot of weight.\", \"id\": \"opus100_stream_000058\", \"pt\": \"Perdeste imenso peso.\", \"source\": \"Helsinki-NLP/opus-100/en-pt/train\"}\n./results/02_final_training/final_training_20260620T053855Z/data_splits/train.jsonl:60:{\"en\": \"Oh, you strong.\", \"id\": \"opus100_stream_000059\", \"pt\": \"Oh, é forte.\", \"source\": \"Helsinki-NLP/opus-100/en-pt/train\"}\n./results/02_final_training/final_training_20260620T053855Z/data_splits/train.jsonl:61:{\"en\": \"I asked you about your family.\", \"id\": \"opus100_stream_000060\", \"pt\": \"Perguntei-te sobre a tua família.\", \"source\": \"Helsinki-NLP/opus-100/en-pt/train\"}\n./results/02_final_training/final_training_20260620T053855Z/data_splits/train.jsonl:62:{\"en\": \"That you chose to save me instead of her.\", \"id\": \"opus100_stream_000061\", \"pt\": \"Que optaste salvar-me em vez dela.\", \"source\": \"Helsinki-NLP/opus-100/en-pt/train\"}\n./results/02_final_training/final_training_20260620T053855Z/data_splits/train.jsonl:63:{\"en\": \"How am I ever going to do great things if I'm stuck here with these silly chickens?\", \"id\": \"opus100_stream_000062\", \"pt\": \"Como vou fazer grandes coisas presa aqui...\", \"source\": \"Helsinki-NLP/opus-100/en-pt/train\"}\n./results/02_final_training/final_training_20260620T053855Z/data_splits/train.jsonl:64:{\"en\": \"I have no idea.\", \"id\": \"opus100_stream_000063\", \"pt\": \"Não faço ideia.\", \"source\": \"Helsinki-NLP/opus-100/en-pt/train\"}\n./results/02_final_training/final_training_20260620T053855Z/data_splits/train.jsonl:65:{\"en\": \"Mel. this time I have something.\", \"id\": \"opus100_stream_000064\", \"pt\": \"Mel. Desta vez tenho alguma coisa.\", \"source\": \"Helsinki-NLP/opus-100/en-pt/train\"}\n./results/02_final_training/final_training_20260620T053855Z/data_splits/train.jsonl:66:{\"en\": \"There are hundreds of names here.\", \"id\": \"opus100_stream_000065\", \"pt\": \"Estão aqui centenas de nomes.\", \"source\": \"Helsinki-NLP/opus-100/en-pt/train\"}\n./results/02_final_training/final_training_20260620T053855Z/data_splits/train.jsonl:67:{\"en\": \"That by sleeping with a future king, you had no idea that you'd be handing over your freedom, freedom to choose your own suitor.\", \"id\": \"opus100_stream_000066\", \"pt\": \"Que dormindo com um futuro rei, não tivestes ideia de que estaríeis a entregar vossa liberdade. A liberdade de escolher vosso próprio pretendente.\", \"source\": \"Helsinki-NLP/opus-100/en-pt/train\"}\n./results/02_final_training/final_training_20260620T053855Z/data_splits/train.jsonl:68:{\"en\": \"- I don't wanna be a money watchdog here... but if you did build everything-- I say this metaphorically-- it'd have to be done over my dead body-- metaphorically.\", \"id\": \"opus100_stream_000067\", \"pt\": \"não é que eu seja um sovina mas se construísses tudo... digo isto metaforicamente... teria que ser feito por cima do meu cadáver...metaforicamente.\", \"source\": \"Helsinki-NLP/opus-100/en-pt/train\"}\n./results/02_final_training/final_training_20260620T053855Z/data_splits/train.jsonl:69:{\"en\": \"- I have to take this.\", \"id\": \"opus100_stream_000068\", \"pt\": \"- Tenho que atender.\", \"source\": \"Helsinki-NLP/opus-100/en-pt/train\"}\n./results/02_final_training/final_training_20260620T053855Z/data_splits/train.jsonl:70:{\"en\": \"We'll take care of this.\", \"id\": \"opus100_stream_000069\", \"pt\": \"Nós tratamos disto.\", \"source\": \"Helsinki-NLP/opus-100/en-pt/train\"}\n./results/02_final_training/final_training_20260620T053855Z/data_splits/train.jsonl:71:{\"en\": \"And I want you to see one card.\", \"id\": \"opus100_stream_000070\", \"pt\": \"E quero que vejas uma carta.\", \"source\": \"Helsinki-NLP/opus-100/en-pt/train\"}\n./results/02_final_training/final_training_20260620T053855Z/data_splits/train.jsonl:72:{\"en\": \"It reminded me of when I was young and stupid.\", \"id\": \"opus100_stream_000071\", \"pt\": \"Lembrou-me de quando eu era novo e estúpido.\", \"source\": \"Helsinki-NLP/opus-100/en-pt/train\"}\n./results/02_final_training/final_training_20260620T053855Z/data_splits/train.jsonl:73:{\"en\": \"Look at you, you look awful.\", \"id\": \"opus100_stream_000072\", \"pt\": \"Olha para ti, estás horrível.\", \"source\": \"Helsinki-NLP/opus-100/en-pt/train\"}\n./results/02_final_training/final_training_20260620T053855Z/data_splits/train.jsonl:74:{\"en\": \"He's gonna gather my plaintiffs, scare them, and then give them a lowball offer.\", \"id\": \"opus100_stream_000073\", \"pt\": \"Vai reunir os meus queixosos, assustá-los e fazer-lhes uma proposta baixa.\", \"source\": \"Helsinki-NLP/opus-100/en-pt/train\"}\n./results/02_final_training/final_training_20260620T053855Z/data_splits/train.jsonl:75:{\"en\": \"She wanted me to send her regards.\", \"id\": \"opus100_stream_000074\", \"pt\": \"Ela manda-lhe um abraço.\", \"source\": \"Helsinki-NLP/opus-100/en-pt/train\"}\n./results/02_final_training/final_training_20260620T053855Z/data_splits/train.jsonl:76:{\"en\": \"I'm isolating each print according to its chemical composition.\", \"id\": \"opus100_stream_000075\", \"pt\": \"Analiso-as de acordo com a composição química.\", \"source\": \"Helsinki-NLP/opus-100/en-pt/train\"}\n./results/02_final_training/final_training_20260620T053855Z/data_splits/train.jsonl:77:{\"en\": \"What if one of these names...?\", \"id\": \"opus100_stream_000076\", \"pt\": \"E se um destes nomes...?\", \"source\": \"Helsinki-NLP/opus-100/en-pt/train\"}\n./results/02_final_training/final_training_20260620T053855Z/data_splits/train.jsonl:78:{\"en\": \"- You're not.\", \"id\": \"opus100_stream_000077\", \"pt\": \"Mas não manda.\", \"source\": \"Helsinki-NLP/opus-100/en-pt/train\"}\n./results/02_final_training/final_training_20260620T053855Z/data_splits/train.jsonl:79:{\"en\": \"Sorry, Frank.\", \"id\": \"opus100_stream_000078\", \"pt\": \"Lamento, Frank.\", \"source\": \"Helsinki-NLP/opus-100/en-pt/train\"}\n./results/02_final_training/final_training_20260620T053855Z/data_splits/train.jsonl:80:{\"en\": \"That guy crashed 10 minutes after he got in there.\", \"id\": \"opus100_stream_000079\", \"pt\": \"A paragem cardíaca ocorreu 10 minutos depois de ele chegar.\", \"source\": \"Helsinki-NLP/opus-100/en-pt/train\"}\n./results/02_final_training/final_training_20260620T053855Z/data_splits/train.jsonl:81:{\"en\": \"And he's about to get robbed.\", \"id\": \"opus100_stream_000080\", \"pt\": \"E está prestes a ser roubado.\", \"source\": \"Helsinki-NLP/opus-100/en-pt/train\"}\n./results/02_final_training/final_training_20260620T053855Z/data_splits/train.jsonl:82:{\"en\": \"That was completely different.\", \"id\": \"opus100_stream_000081\", \"pt\": \"- Isso foi diferente.\", \"source\": \"Helsinki-NLP/opus-100/en-pt/train\"}\n./results/02_final_training/final_training_20260620T053855Z/data_splits/train.jsonl:83:{\"en\": \"0.99, 1.18; 42 trials and 8167 patients).\", \"id\": \"opus100_stream_000082\", \"pt\": \"0, 99 - 1, 18; 42 estudos e 8167 doentes).\", \"source\": \"Helsinki-NLP/opus-100/en-pt/train\"}\n./results/02_final_training/final_training_20260620T053855Z/data_splits/train.jsonl:84:{\"en\": \"Because other girls liked it and they thought it was funny. That's all.\", \"id\": \"opus100_stream_000083\", \"pt\": \"Porque as outras meninas gostaram e acharam engraçado, só isso.\", \"source\": \"Helsinki-NLP/opus-100/en-pt/train\"}\n./results/02_final_training/final_training_20260620T053855Z/data_splits/train.jsonl:85:{\"en\": \"Merry Christmas.\", \"id\": \"opus100_stream_000084\", \"pt\": \"Feliz Natal.\", \"source\": \"Helsinki-NLP/opus-100/en-pt/train\"}\n./results/02_final_training/final_training_20260620T053855Z/data_splits/train.jsonl:86:{\"en\": \"It matters not.\", \"id\": \"opus100_stream_000085\", \"pt\": \"Tal não importa.\", \"source\": \"Helsinki-NLP/opus-100/en-pt/train\"}\n./results/02_final_training/final_training_20260620T053855Z/data_splits/train.jsonl:87:{\"en\": \"Oh, don't worry, honey.\", \"id\": \"opus100_stream_000086\", \"pt\": \"Não te preocupes, querido.\", \"source\": \"Helsinki-NLP/opus-100/en-pt/train\"}\n./results/02_final_training/final_training_20260620T053855Z/data_splits/train.jsonl:88:{\"en\": \"Prepare to fire!\", \"id\": \"opus100_stream_000087\", \"pt\": \"Preparar setas!\", \"source\": \"Helsinki-NLP/opus-100/en-pt/train\"}\n./results/02_final_training/final_training_20260620T053855Z/data_splits/train.jsonl:89:{\"en\": \"- What's all this stuff?\", \"id\": \"opus100_stream_000088\", \"pt\": \"O que são estas coisas?\", \"source\": \"Helsinki-NLP/opus-100/en-pt/train\"}\n./results/02_final_training/final_training_20260620T053855Z/data_splits/train.jsonl:90:{\"en\": \"(S)-N-5-[2-(2-amino-4-oxo-4,6,7,8-tetrahydro-1H-pyrimido[5,4-b][1,4]thiazin-6-yl)ethyl-2-thenoyl]-L-glutamic acid\", \"id\": \"opus100_stream_000089\", \"pt\": \"ácido (S)