lvo.\", \"source\": \"Helsinki-NLP/opus-100/en-pt/train\"}\n./results/02_final_training/final_training_20260620T053855Z/data_splits/validation.jsonl:2:{\"en\": \"This Regulation shall be binding in its entirety and directly applicable in all Member States.\", \"id\": \"opus100_stream_000097\", \"pt\": \"O presente regulamento é obrigatório em todos os seus elementos e directamente aplicável em todos os Estados-membros.\", \"source\": \"Helsinki-NLP/opus-100/en-pt/train\"}\n./results/02_final_training/final_training_20260620T053855Z/data_splits/validation.jsonl:3:{\"en\": \"NACE 23.64: Manufacture of mortars\", \"id\": \"opus100_stream_000098\", \"pt\": \"NACE 23.64: Fabricação de argamassas\", \"source\": \"Helsinki-NLP/opus-100/en-pt/train\"}\n./results/02_final_training/final_training_20260620T053855Z/data_splits/validation.jsonl:4:{\"en\": \"What if I had another confession to make?\", \"id\": \"opus100_stream_000099\", \"pt\": \"- E se tiver outra confissão a fazer?\", \"source\": \"Helsinki-NLP/opus-100/en-pt/train\"}\n./results/02_final_training/final_training_20260620T053855Z/data_splits/validation.jsonl:5:{\"en\": \"of 31 January 2006\", \"id\": \"opus100_stream_000100\", \"pt\": \"de 31 de Janeiro de 2006\", \"source\": \"Helsinki-NLP/opus-100/en-pt/train\"}\n./results/02_final_training/final_training_20260620T053855Z/data_splits/validation.jsonl:6:{\"en\": \"There ain't gonna be any show tonight, or anytime soon.\", \"id\": \"opus100_stream_000101\", \"pt\": \"Não haverá espetáculo hoje à noite. Nem tão cedo haverá.\", \"source\": \"Helsinki-NLP/opus-100/en-pt/train\"}\n./results/02_final_training/final_training_20260620T053855Z/data_splits/validation.jsonl:7:{\"en\": \"What is that program?\", \"id\": \"opus100_stream_000102\", \"pt\": \"Que Programa é aquele?\", \"source\": \"Helsinki-NLP/opus-100/en-pt/train\"}\n./results/02_final_training/final_training_20260620T053855Z/data_splits/validation.jsonl:8:{\"en\": \"I'm talking about a tournament.\", \"id\"